<paragraph id="8BBE950CFFB9F77CF2C8FF7BECA1D0C9" blockId="2.[151,1436,151,213]" pageId="2" pageNumber="86">
<emphasis id="B975491EFFB9F77CF2C8FF7BEF73D0AD" bold="true" box="[151,267,151,177]" pageId="2" pageNumber="86">Remarks.</emphasis>
The two subgenera of 
<taxonomicName id="4C01EE8FFFB9F77CF052FF7BECE6D0AD" authorityName="Fairmaire" authorityYear="1881" box="[525,670,151,177]" class="Insecta" family="Lycidae" genus="Helcophorus" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="2" pageNumber="86" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">
