</taxonomicName>
are distinguishable, in addition to the structure of male genitalia, by the eye size and elytral vestiture (
<bibRefCitation id="EF90E8FDFFB9F77CF051FF57ECB5D0C9" author="Kazantsev, S. V." box="[526,717,186,213]" pageId="2" pageNumber="86" pagination="383 - 389" refId="ref2761" refString="Kazantsev, S. V. (2015) New taxa of Helcophorus Fairmaire, 1891, with a key to species of the genus (Coleoptera: Lycidae). In: Hartmann, M. &amp; Weipert, J. (Eds.), Biodiversitat und Naturausstattung im Himalaya. Band 5. Verein der Freunde &amp; Forderer des Naturkundemuseums Erfurt e. V., Erfurt, pp. 383 - 389." type="book chapter" year="2015">Kazantsev, 2015</bibRefCitation>
